Namu Amida Butsu,</i>

38:52.881 --> 38:54.940
<i>Namu Amida Butsu...</i>

39:48.904 --> 39:49.736
Chester...

39:49.813 --> 39:51.830
Leave me.

39:51.907 --> 39:53.957
Please.

